entries.femaleVariant: Por dios, these kids don't know shit...
<mothertongue l="mex" m="chavos de la calle" b="Yeah, not like the " a=" – ain't no better school than the streets."/>

<mothertongue l="mex" m="Pinches chavos..." b="" a=" They come to me – the baddest <Rich color=\"MainColors.ActiveBlue\">cabrón</> on the block – for free samples? Free?! Where the fuck they get that idea from, eh?"/>
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Sí" b="" a=", or the media."/>
There is no such thing as "free" in this life.
Ey, man, you preachin' to the converted.
